data.description: AKA: 2200 Faunce Street. Rarely offered Solid Brick Rhawnhurst Corner Single-Detached Rancher! Separate entrances (1 on Faunce Street into center foyer & 1 on Horrocks St. through finished lower level). 1-car driveway to 1-car attached garage, in-law suite style finished lower level complete with LR, kitchenette, & wet bar.
data.whatILove:
Its in a great neighborhood consisting of Hard working individuals in their thirties and older. Children are mainly older high school age and well behaved. Conveniently located near shopping, public transportation and main highways.
Completely renovated first floor, Beautifully finished entertainment area with ceramic floors and real pine tongue and groove 2wood walls sealed with polyurethane. A brand new 12" wet bar with brass foot rails makes the home perfect for entertaining friends and family. A private stairway leads from the entertainment room to the rear yard where a Palegra (trellis,) 16"x 12', was added just last spring. Cozy and comfortable.
